<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ش ت ر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٧٥٧ - ش ت ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شتَرَ يَشتِر، شَتْرًا، فهو شاتر، والمفعول مَشْتور<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شتَر ثوبَه:</span> قطعه ومزّقه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• شتَر فلانًا:</span> جرحَه <span class="c1">"شتَر السِّكّينُ إصبعَ الجزّار"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>